name: Vladia Trinh
about: Hi! I’m Vladia. I am an Operations Research major with a minor in Computer Science. On DTI, I hope to make a positive impact on Cornell and its surrounding community through engineering. Here, I am a member of Alpha Phi Omega, and tutor middle schoolers in Ithaca. I love to travel and explore new places almost as much as I enjoy staying home and making coffee. In my free time, you can catch me watching Grey’s Anatomy, getting Korean food in college town, or FaceTiming my dog.
